snippet.title: Madden NFL 10 - Titans vs. Ravens - HD (1 of 6)
snippet.description:
Watch as the Titans (controlled by Madden lead designer Ian Cummings) take on the CPU Ravens in this epic Wild card playoff battle thanks to Madden NFL 10.
- 10 minute quarters w/ accelerated clock
- All-Pro difficulty
- Default slider settings

*** DISCLAIMER ***
This is an Alpha build and the game is still work in progress.
